name: jaspr_ui
desc: Export file for the UI components library.

name: Accordion

name: style

desc: The title displayed in the accordion header.

desc: Defines the visual style of an accordion item.

name: AccordionStyle
desc: Creates an AccordionStyle with an associated CSS class name.

name: className
desc: Returns the CSS class name associated with this accordion style.

name: Button
desc:
A collection of button components for building user interfaces with Jaspr.
These components provide different button styles while maintaining a consistent API.
A standard button component that renders a basic button with customizable styling.

name: Button
desc: Creates a new Button instance.

name: attributes
desc: Optional map of additional HTML attributes to apply to the button element

name: build
desc: Describes the part of the user interface represented by this component.

name: color
desc: Optional color theme for the button from ButtonColor

name: onPressed
desc: Optional callback function triggered when the button is clicked

name: size
desc: The size of the button from ButtonSize, defaults to ButtonSize.normal

name: title
desc: The text to display on the button

name: ButtonColor
desc: Button colors for styling UI components

name: className
desc: Returns the CSS class name associated with this button color

name: values
desc: A constant List of the values in this enum, in order of their declaration.

name: ButtonWithBadge
desc: A clickable button with an embedded badge component.

name: ButtonWithBadge
desc: Creates a new button with badge instance.

desc: Describes the part of the user interface represented by this component.

name: color
desc:
Optional color variant for the badge
If not specified, uses the default badge styling

name: onPressed
desc: Callback function that is called when the button is pressed

name: title
desc: The text label/title for the button

name: total
desc: The numeric value or total to display in the badge
